OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1671980104
OL,6,GOfcom says it will engage with the BBC
OL,7,Gas it develops its plans for the
OL,8,Gcombined BBC News service and changes
OL,9,Gto BBC Local Radio.
OL,11,FIn its latest annual report on the BBC,
OL,12,Fthe broadcasting regulator said the BBC
OL,13,Fmust continue to "deliver content for
OL,14,Fall audiences in the UK", including the
OL,15,Fprovision of "UK and international news
OL,16,Fand current affairs for domestic TV and
OL,17,Fonline audiences".
OL,3,COfcom scrutinises BBC News and Local
OL,4,CRadio changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G1/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34902
SC,0002
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1671980104
OL,6,FThe BBC plans to combine the current
OL,7,FBBC News Channel and BBC World News TV
OL,8,Fservice into a single channel from
OL,9,FApril 2023.
OL,11,FUK viewers will see simulcasts of news
OL,12,Fprogrammes on BBC One and BBC Two in
OL,13,Fplace of World News programming. At
OL,14,Fother times, the BBC says there is an
OL,15,F"option" to opt-out of the main service
OL,16,Fto provide UK-specific content.
OL,3,COfcom scrutinises BBC News and Local
OL,4,CRadio changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G2/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34903
SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1671980104
OL,6,FThe plans, which have not gone to
OL,7,Fpublic consultation, have raised fears
OL,8,Fthat the TV news channel will
OL,9,Fdeprioritise UK news ` something that
OL,10,Fhas already become evident in recent
OL,11,Fweeks as more of its UK-focused news
OL,12,Foutput is replaced by World News
OL,13,Fsimulcasts.
OL,3,COfcom scrutinises BBC News and Local
OL,4,CRadio changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G3/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34904
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1671980104
OL,6,FAccording to Ofcom, the BBC is "still
OL,7,Fin the process of developing its plans
OL,8,Ffor the integration of the two
OL,9,Fservices." But Ofcom added: "it is
OL,10,Fimportant that the BBC continues to
OL,11,Foffer a broad range of domestic news
OL,12,Ffor UK audiences who rely on broadcast
OL,13,Fservices".
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Ofcom has warned the BBC it
OL,16,Fis closely following the broadcaster's
OL,17,Fcontroversial plans for local radio.
OL,3,COfcom scrutinises BBC News and Local
OL,4,CRadio changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G4/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34905
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1671980104
OL,6,FThe BBC recently announced plans to cut
OL,7,Flocal radio output to eight hours
OL,8,FMonday ` Friday, with regional and
OL,9,Fnational programming outside of local
OL,10,Flive sports coverage at other times.
OL,12,FOfcom said it would monitor the
OL,13,Fstations between which the BBC shares
OL,14,Fits programming, as well as the
OL,15,Fspecific programming being shared.
OL,16,FOfcom said it intended to do this going
OL,17,Fforward "to ensure that the BBC
OL,18,Fcontinues to provide important local
OL,19,Fcontent such as local news".
OL,3,COfcom scrutinises BBC News and Local
OL,4,CRadio changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G5/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34906
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1671980104
OL,6,FOfcom confirmed for the second time
OL,7,Fthis year that if it had any concerns
OL,8,Fabout the BBC's delivery of news and
OL,9,Fcurrent affairs as a result of planned
OL,10,Fchanges, it could amend the Operating
OL,11,FLicence to enable it to hold the BBC to
OL,12,Faccount.
OL,14,FElsewhere in Ofcom's report, the
OL,15,Fregulator found the BBC was failing at
OL,16,Freaching out to audiences on lower
OL,17,Fincomes, including semi or low-skilled
OL,18,Fworkers and people on state benefits.
OL,3,COfcom scrutinises BBC News and Local
OL,4,CRadio changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G6/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34907
SC,0007
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1671980104
OL,6,FPeople in lower socio-economic groups
OL,7,Fwere more likely to have a poor opinion
OL,8,Fon the BBC's output, according to
OL,9,FOfcom's research.
OL,11,FAnd Ofcom ordered changes in the way
OL,12,Fthe BBC communicates planned changes to
OL,13,Fits services. The regulator demanded
OL,14,Fgreater consistency. But some future
OL,15,Fchanges will not need to go out to
OL,16,Fconsultation and won't need Ofcom's
OL,17,Finvolvement.
OL,3,COfcom scrutinises BBC News and Local
OL,4,CRadio changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G7/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34908
SC,0008
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F349A1671980104
OL,6,FDocuments released by Ofcom today
OL,7,Findicate changes to services including
OL,8,Fthe iPlayer and BBC Sounds are less
OL,9,Flikely to need additional scrutiny.
OL,10,FThat's a move that could make it easier
OL,11,Ffor the BBC to launch pop-up
OL,12,Fonline-only TV and radio streams.
OL,3,COfcom scrutinises BBC News and Local
OL,4,CRadio changes
